To build and run the web app:

    yarn install
    yarn build
    yarn run http-server -p 8080 docs

To publish:

    yarn build:release
    git update-index --no-skip-worktree docs/main.js*
    git commit -a -m 'Publish' && git push
    git update-index --skip-worktree docs/main.js*

